content: This app is useless. Such a money trap.

Works flawlessly on my s8+! Smart to be able to get this info from a phone 
instead of carrying extra items.

Hands-down the BEST inclinometer app for avalanche assessment!  Unique voice and "lock" features allow for sighting angles up-slope and down-slope, as well as cross-slope.  Allows easy logging of slope angle measurements by location for later reference.  Clean & simple interface makes for quick & easy use in the field.  REALLY slick!
Useful, however cannot turn sound off.  On/off switch turns itself back on.
replyContent: When running the Avalanche Inclinometer, choose Settings at the bottom of the screen (the "gear" icon) and then set "Enable Speech" to off.
